ass='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#set-strong-passwords\" title=\"Set Strong Passwords\">Set Strong Passwords<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#use-your-mobile-phone\" title=\"Use Your Mobile phone\">Use Your Mobile phone<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#be-smart-when-shopping\" title=\"Be Smart When Shopping\">Be Smart When Shopping<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#check-at-the-companys-return-policy\" title=\"Check at the Company\u2019s Return Policy\">Check at the Company\u2019s Return Policy<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#how-to-tell-if-a-website-is-secure\" title=\"How to Tell If a Website is Secure\">How to Tell If a Website is Secure<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#what-are-some-of-the-ways-to-pay-online\" title=\"What Are Some of the Ways to Pay Online?\">What Are Some of the Ways to Pay Online?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#paypal\" title=\"PayPal\">PayPal<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#shop-pay\" title=\"Shop Pay\">Shop Pay<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/online-purchases-how-to-stay-safe-on-the-web\/#what-is-the-best-payment-option\" title=\"What is the Best Payment Option?\">What is the Best Payment Option?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"introduction\"><\/span>Introduction<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Today millions of people shop online as many businesses are situated there. This means that companies and customers must carry out their transactions via online financial services. The problem is that there are so many hackers and scammers online who take advantage of businesses and customers who don\u2019t understand how to make online purchases safely.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When shopping online, it is crucial to consider security and safety before any other thing. You can use so many indicators to determine if you are making your financial transaction on a legit site. This post will provide more insights on safe online shopping tips and how to conduct your online transactions to avoid losing your money.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"how-online-payments-work\"><\/span>How Online Payments Work<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When making an online payment, there are several parties involved in promoting safe online purchases. Legit websites usually add the best payments solution to their website to ensure customers do not get scammed and increase customer confidence. When you pay online, these are the parties involved in the transaction:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 The seller: the seller is the person who is offering the products you are purchasing.<br>\u2022 The company: this is the seller\u2019s website or where the business is situated.<br>\u2022 Payment Gateway: this is the software that is behind the sellers\u2019 online website. <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-multiple-payment-gateways-help-merchants-sell\/#:~:text=Anyone%20looking%20to%20expand%20their%20business%20to%20a%20global%20scale%20should%20consider%20whether%20their%20current%20payment%20provider%20can%20handle%20such%20a%20shift.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Payment gateways<\/a> handle online transactions and securely send your payment information to the processing company.<br>\u2022 A processing company: also known as the acquirer. It is where your payments are processed.<br>\u2022 A Payment Scheme: the payment scheme is what your card is linked to. It could be PayPal or Visa. It also forms a link between the issuing bank and the acquirer.<br>\u2022 The Bank: the bank provides you with a credit or debit card.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-pros-and-cons-of-online-payment\"><\/span>The pros and Cons of Online Payment<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"pros\"><\/span>Pros<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 It improves speed and efficiency<br>\u2022 Minimizes transaction costs<br>\u2022 Saves time<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cons\"><\/span>Cons<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Frauds and scams are present<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tips-for-secure-online-shopping\"><\/span>Tips for Secure Online Shopping<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the safest payment method is <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pcmag.com\/how-to\/14-tips-for-safe-online-shopping\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">not the only thing you should do<\/a> when you shop online. There are also other safe online shopping tips to consider to ensure your money ends up in the correct place. They include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"use-legitimate-websites\"><\/span>Use Legitimate Websites<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When shopping online, make sure you use reputable companies. Some websites are set up to collect customers\u2019 card details, while others are there to take your money. It is important to look for the products you want on familiar websites. This is one way how to stay safe when shopping online.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"avoid-public-wi-fi\"><\/span>Avoid Public Wi-Fi<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To make safe online purchases, use private networks. Public Wi-Fi is rarely trusted as your information can easily be hacked.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"set-strong-passwords\"><\/span>Set Strong Passwords<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Strong passwords can help ensure that your card details are safe. Look at the tips of setting a strong password. Password managers can be of great help if you are not good at creating unique passwords.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"use-your-mobile-phone\"><\/span>Use Your Mobile phone<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Is it safe to buy things using your phone? Your phone makes it easier for you to carry out online purchases. This is because you can use payment apps like PayPal to make purchases directly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But even when using your phone, you should use safety tips to avoid hackers, such as installing a VPN in your phone. Also, using your phone is much more secure than issuing your credit card details. It is the best way to pay online without credit card.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/tips-for-secure-onliine-purchases-1.jpg\" alt=\"online purchases\" class=\"