, it will turn green<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"what-are-some-of-the-ways-to-pay-online\"><\/span>What Are Some of the Ways to Pay Online?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are several payments solutions you can use to make safe online purchases. Some of these options are considered the safest way to receive money from a stranger online and will work perfectly well for you. They include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"paypal\"><\/span>PayPal<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are asking, \u201cWhat is the safest way to receive money from a buyer?\u201d PayPal has got you covered. PayPal is one of the most popular online payment solutions used by many online sellers to receive money. The good thing with PayPal is that it allows you to connect your credit card or bank account. This allows you to transfer money faster and securely.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"shop-pay\"><\/span>Shop Pay<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is another best way to pay online without a credit card. It is an in-built system that protects your card and is mainly used by Shopify merchants.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"what-is-the-best-payment-option\"><\/span>What is the Best Payment Option?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are several payment options you can use when making online purchases. All you need to do is use the correct tips when shopping online. Also, look at the website you are using to buy products. Do not enter your card details on any website that you do not trust.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If something does not go right, contact the bank immediately to ensure your card is not used for fraudulent activities.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Introduction Today millions of people shop online as many businesses are situated there. This means that companies and 